column10: term creaor URI (e.g. ORCID, for multiple contributors use ‘|‘ as seperator)
column12: editor note (additional comments by the term curators, such as more elaborated obsoletion reasons)
column13: obsoletion reason → choose one of these possible values: 'failed exploratory term', 'placeholder removed', 'terms merged', 'term imported', 'term split', 'out of scope'
